WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:01:07.600 --> 00:01:09.600
What are you doing?

00:01:13.480 --> 00:01:15.480
Now , Fern,  Go back to bed

00:01:15.480 --> 00:01:16.860
You're not going to kill it, are you?

00:01:16.860 --> 00:01:17.920
It's just a runt.  Now, go back to bed.

00:01:20.180 --> 00:01:22.180
No, it's not fair.  It can't help being born small.

00:01:22.180 --> 00:01:23.160
Careful!

00:01:23.160 --> 00:01:25.160
If I'd been born small , would you kill me?

00:01:26.840 --> 00:01:28.840
Of course not.

00:01:31.380 --> 00:01:33.380
A little girl is one thing.  A runty pig is another

00:01:34.060 --> 00:01:36.060
It's no different!

00:01:36.240 --> 00:01:38.240
It's unfair and unjust.

00:01:39.340 --> 00:01:41.340
How can you be so heartless?

00:01:43.940 --> 00:01:48.720
Come here.  I want to show you something.  You see that?  You see?   Eleven pigs and only ten teats.

00:01:48.900 --> 00:01:51.720
The sow can't feed it , honey.

00:01:52.040 --> 00:01:54.040
Then I will

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:05.000
(to Wilbur)  I'll feed you . . .and take care of you. . .

00:02:09.340 --> 00:02:11.340
(to her father) I absolutely will not let you kill him.

